      intro T S
      funext v
      simp [lineDerivCLM]
      all_goals try { simp [add_assoc] }
      <;> try { tauto }
    map_smul' := by
      intro T c
      funext v
      simp [lineDerivCLM]
      all_goals try { simp [mul_add, mul_assoc] }
      <;> try { tauto }
    cont := by
      apply Continuous.continuous
      apply Continuous.comp
      · exact lineDerivCLM.continuous
      · exact T.continuous
  }
```

This completes the proof by defining all the necessary components of the linear map `fderivCLM`.
