        apply Continuous.continuousLinearMap
        all_goals try { continuity }
        all_goals try { aesop }
        all_goals try { tauto }
        all_goals try { norm_num }
        all_goals try { tauto }
        all_goals try { aesop }
        all_goals try { tauto }
    ```

